Package de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData

Record Class AgentDebugData

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData.AgentDebugData
Record Components:
name - the name of the agent
supervisor - the supervisor of the agent
role - the current role of the agent
energy - the current energy of the agent
lastAction - the last performed action of the agent
lastActionSuccess - the action request result of the last action
lastActionDesire - the desire which generated the last action
groupDesireType - the current group desire of the agent
groupDesirePartner - the name of the team mate which performs a group desire with the agent
groupDesireBlock - the block on which the group desire is based on
attachedThings - a String containing information about the attached things to the agent
public record AgentDebugData(String name, String supervisor, String role, int energy, String lastAction, String lastActionSuccess, String lastActionDesire, String groupDesireType, String groupDesirePartner, String groupDesireBlock, String attachedThings) extends Record
The Record AgentDebugData provides a data structure to store information about an agent.
Author:
Heinz Stadler
